üßë‚Äçü§ù‚Äçüßë Dimension: Gold.dim_customers

Purpose: Contains customer master data enriched with demographics and location.
Grain: One row per unique customer.

  | Column            | Description                               | Example    |
| ----------------- | ----------------------------------------- | ---------- |
| `customer_key`    | Surrogate key (internal DW key for joins) | 1          |
| `customer_id`     | Business key (CRM ID)                     | 101        |
| `customer_number` | CRM customer code                         | CUST-A001  |
| `first_name`      | Customer‚Äôs first name                     | John       |
| `last_name`       | Customer‚Äôs last name                      | Smith      |
| `country`         | Country from ERP location                 | USA        |
| `maritial_status` | Marital status                            | Married    |
| `gender`          | Gender (CRM is master, ERP fallback)      | Male       |
| `birthdate`       | Date of birth                             | 1985-06-22 |
| `create_date`     | Customer creation date in CRM             | 2018-03-01 |

  üëâ Example Use Case: Find all customers from "USA" created in the last 5 years.
