  üì¶ Dimension: Gold.dim_products

Purpose: Stores product master data enriched with categories and costs.
Grain: One row per unique product.

  | Column           | Description                               | Example           |
| ---------------- | ----------------------------------------- | ----------------- |
| `product_key`    | Surrogate key (internal DW key for joins) | 10                |
| `product_id`     | Business key (CRM product ID)             | 2001              |
| `product_number` | CRM product code                          | PRD-001           |
| `product_name`   | Name of product                           | iPhone 14         |
| `category_id`    | ERP category ID                           | CAT-01            |
| `category`       | Product category                          | Electronics       |
| `subcategory`    | Product sub-category                      | Mobile Phones     |
| `maintenance`    | Maintenance type from ERP                 | Standard Warranty |
| `cost`           | Product cost                              | 699               |
| `product_line`   | Product line                              | Mobile Devices    |
| `start_date`     | Product activation/start date             | 2022-09-01        |

  üëâ Example Use Case: Analyze sales by category or subcategory (e.g., "How many phones sold vs laptops?").
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    üí∞ Fact: Gold.fact_sales

Purpose: Records sales transactions, linked to customers and products.
Grain: One row per order line item (customer √ó product √ó order).
  
| Column         | Description                                                | Example    |
| -------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- | ---------- |
| `order_number` | Sales order number                                         | SO-5001    |
| `product_key`  | Surrogate product key (FK ‚Üí `dim_products.product_key`)    | 10         |
| `customer_key` | Surrogate customer key (FK ‚Üí `dim_customers.customer_key`) | 1          |
| `order_date`   | Order date                                                 | 2023-02-10 |
| `ship_date`    | Shipping date                                              | 2023-02-12 |
| `due_date`     | Due date                                                   | 2023-02-15 |
| `sales_amount` | Total sales amount for this line                           | 1398       |
| `quantity`     | Number of units ordered                                    | 2          |
| `price`        | Unit price                                                 | 699        |

  üëâ Example Use Case:

Total sales by country and category: "What is the sales revenue of Electronics in USA for 2023?"

Customer lifetime value: "How much has John Smith purchased in total since joining?"
